The paper deals with the design of a secure communication system, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network security (cs.CR). The system is a multiuser system, which involves networking and communication (cs.NI). The proposed algorithm is a low-complexity algorithm, which involves system optimization and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper presents numerical results, which involve signal processing and machine learning (cs.MM).
